          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The auditorium was amazing, showcasing talented students who expressed their hidden talents.",
          "name": "Hana Shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the notices were pre-uploaded to the website without fail, which was one of the best things.",
          "name": "Hana Shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "As it is located in a prime location , means of transport are easy to catch",
          "name": "John Quadras",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "College campus , canteen area and there is a garden as well outside of the college , so the overalll environment around the college is peaco",
          "name": "John Quadras",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Work with nss unit and felt great  and loved the atmosphere of the college has great bonding with teachers few teachers had supported and strong support and also a great behaviour and always feel like home best college life I ever had in Mumbai thank",
          "name": "Abhay rajgure",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college organizations is very disciplined",
          "name": "Turab Ali Dhaga",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The canteen food is so good, just like home made one.",
          "name": "Anonymous",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The classes have Air conditioners and Projectors",
          "name": "Vansh Vinod Kothari",
          "course_tag_name": "BMS"
        },
        {
          "text": "College celebrates many events and fests every year for the students",
          "name": "Lattesh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "teacher was not on time we used to sit and wait 1 or 2 hours for her to start the lecture",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "forced to attend events, guest lectures.",
          "name": "Review guru",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I didnt like the infrastructure, quality of the class",
          "name": "Hana Shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Parking facilities were often inadequate, causing delays while searching for a place to park our vehicle during exams.",
          "name": "Hana Shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "So there’s no guarantee of placement from the college",
          "name": "John Quadras",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement cell provides internship but generally it doesn’t provide stipends",
          "name": "John Quadras",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Dirty toilets not available with sanitization for washing hands in boys restroom and had unreal working time of college office staff irritating elevator peon, not proper department communication present which effect each other event and lab is bad to",
